1
00:00:51,399 --> 00:00:52,640
Sir, checking out apartments?

2
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:54,600
Are you looking to rent or buy?

3
00:00:55,280 --> 00:00:56,200
There are three of us in the family.

4
00:00:56,520 --> 00:00:57,880
We wanna move somewhere bigger.

5
00:00:58,399 --> 00:00:59,200
Three bedrooms, two living rooms.

6
00:00:59,799 --> 00:01:00,280
With an elevator.

7
00:01:00,880 --> 00:01:02,000
It's not a high floor.

8
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:04,640
But it's south-facing, great light for sure.

9
00:01:05,159 --> 00:01:08,000
Now Xiaobei will have a spacious place.

10
00:01:08,840 --> 00:01:10,239
Sir, here at our place...

11
00:01:10,439 --> 00:01:11,400
Renting comes with a great perk.

12
00:01:11,920 --> 00:01:12,599
Zero rent.

13
00:01:12,799 --> 00:01:13,760
Zero rent.

14
00:01:14,640 --> 00:01:15,439
Our company...

15
00:01:15,719 --> 00:01:17,760
uses a Korean-style business model.

16
00:01:18,280 --> 00:01:20,799
You pay us a deposit upfront,

17
00:01:21,079 --> 00:01:21,560
and then we

18
00:01:21,719 --> 00:01:23,200
invest that money.

19
00:01:23,760 --> 00:01:25,239
Stocks and funds make great money.

20
00:01:25,439 --> 00:01:26,239
You know how it is.

21
00:01:27,519 --> 00:01:30,159
That's why we can charge so little

22
00:01:30,319 --> 00:01:31,400
for such a great place.

23
00:01:32,519 --> 00:01:34,519
So how much is the deposit?

24
00:01:34,640 --> 00:01:35,079
Not much.

25
00:01:35,280 --> 00:01:35,879
About 50,000 yuan.

26
00:01:36,719 --> 00:01:38,359
I don't have that kind of money.

27
00:01:39,159 --> 00:01:39,920
No rush, sir.

28
00:01:40,319 --> 00:01:40,920
We've got options.

29
00:01:41,519 --> 00:01:42,120
Our company

30
00:01:42,400 --> 00:01:43,840
has a dedicated loan department.

31
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:45,000
One-stop service.

32
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:45,799
Really?

33
00:01:45,799 --> 00:01:46,439
How about this, sir.

34
00:01:46,920 --> 00:01:48,560
Come in and learn more about it.

35
00:01:48,840 --> 00:01:50,480
I'll walk you through it in detail.

36
00:01:50,959 --> 00:01:51,319
Sure, sure.

37
00:01:51,560 --> 00:01:52,040
Right this way.

38
00:01:52,840 --> 00:01:53,879
Is there really such a good deal?

39
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:54,959
Xiao Li.

40
00:01:55,239 --> 00:01:55,840
Get some hot water.

41
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:56,480
Right this way.

42
00:01:56,760 --> 00:01:58,959
Zhao Zhiqian's peony painting, take a look.

43
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:00,599
Aged Xuan paper.

44
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:01,719
Look at the brushstroke.

45
00:02:01,879 --> 00:02:02,840
It's definitely authentic.

46
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:04,000
I'm telling you,

47
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:05,920
this came straight from the palace.

48
00:02:06,159 --> 00:02:07,359
During the chaos of the war back then,

49
00:02:07,760 --> 00:02:10,000
many maids and eunuchs smuggled things out.

50
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:11,360
My grandpa's grandpa

51
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:12,680
was a palace eunuch at the time.

52
00:02:13,039 --> 00:02:14,319
A top-ranking head eunuch.

53
00:02:14,719 --> 00:02:15,919
He brought this out when he fled.

54
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:17,960
It's our family heirloom.

55
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:20,599
How much are you asking?

56
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:24,759
If I didn't need medical money to stay alive,

57
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:25,840
I'd never sell it.

58
00:02:26,159 --> 00:02:26,800
Name a price.

59
00:02:28,159 --> 00:02:29,159
I'll give you my rock-bottom price.

60
00:02:30,479 --> 00:02:31,000
300,000.

61
00:02:34,039 --> 00:02:36,319
Sir, that painting is fake.

62
00:02:38,120 --> 00:02:39,520
What would a jianbing seller know?

63
00:02:40,199 --> 00:02:40,560
Step aside.

64
00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:43,479
Young man.

65
00:02:43,759 --> 00:02:45,840
Why do you say it's fake?

66
00:02:49,280 --> 00:02:50,000
After more than a hundred years,

67
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:51,759
any seal paste would've dried solid.

68
00:02:52,120 --> 00:02:53,199
It definitely wouldn't wipe off.

69
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:55,560
This seal was stamped a month ago, tops.

70
00:02:57,240 --> 00:02:58,599
Stop pretending you know what you're doing.

71
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:00,800
If you damage my painting,

72
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:02,080
you're paying for it.

73
00:03:02,639 --> 00:03:04,159
This painting costs 300,000 yuan.

74
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:05,879
You're the one pretending to know.

75
00:03:06,719 --> 00:03:07,560
An authentic Zhao Zhiqian

76
00:03:07,560 --> 00:03:08,560
would be worth way more than 300,000.

77
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:13,039
The auction house lists it at 280,000.

78
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:15,599
That's per square foot.

79
00:03:15,879 --> 00:03:17,319
You don't even know how art auctions work,

80
00:03:17,319 --> 00:03:18,439
and you dare to scam people?

81
00:03:18,759 --> 00:03:19,240
Cut the crap.

82
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:19,759
Come on, let's go.

83
00:03:20,039 --> 00:03:20,879
We'll settle this somewhere else.

84
00:03:20,879 --> 00:03:21,319
Enough.

85
00:03:22,479 --> 00:03:23,439
And you, stay out of it.

86
00:03:32,479 --> 00:03:33,800
So it's Master Long.

87
00:03:34,319 --> 00:03:35,199
I was blind.

88
00:03:35,479 --> 00:03:37,159
I made a fool of myself in front of an expert.

89
00:03:38,479 --> 00:03:39,479
Listen to me.

90
00:03:39,599 --> 00:03:42,039
That kid just saved your skin.

91
00:03:42,599 --> 00:03:43,280
Now get out of here.

92
00:03:44,319 --> 00:03:44,719
Thank you, Master Long.

93
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:45,680
And?

94
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:50,960
Thanks for the lesson, kid.

95
00:03:52,960 --> 00:03:54,080
I'll leave you to it. I'll take my leave.

96
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:59,840
Young man, you know your art.

97
00:04:01,639 --> 00:04:02,080
No, I don't.

98
00:04:05,879 --> 00:04:06,560
Long Yi.

99
00:04:08,280 --> 00:04:09,639
Go ask around for me.

100
00:04:09,639 --> 00:04:11,319
About that young jianbing seller.

101
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:12,039
Yes.

102
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:20,399
If it goes up one more day,

103
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:22,959
I'll have enough to buy my parents a home.

104
00:04:36,199 --> 00:04:36,959
Start offloading.

105
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:38,399
Three out, one in.

106
00:04:39,399 --> 00:04:39,839
Remember,

107
00:04:40,839 --> 00:04:42,040
keep it completely under the radar.

108
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:52,560
Sorry, the number you dialed

109
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:53,839
is currently unanswered.

110
00:04:54,879 --> 00:04:57,160
Pick up, pick up!

111
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:00,680
Why did you screw me over?

112
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:05,160
Your dad told me to push the Eggshell Fund on you.

113
00:05:05,759 --> 00:05:06,720
Who would've thought

114
00:05:07,279 --> 00:05:08,600
a father would screw over his own son?

115
00:05:10,959 --> 00:05:12,480
Sheng Shizhong!

116
00:05:16,279 --> 00:05:17,279
Why are you ruining me?

117
00:05:22,079 --> 00:05:23,560
Who gave you the nerve

118
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:25,560
to shout at me?

119
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:27,040
Why did you have Zhu Yutong

120
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:28,560
recommend the Eggshell Fund to me?

121
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:30,000
Why did you short it?

122
00:05:30,519 --> 00:05:31,839
All my money's gone!

123
00:05:35,959 --> 00:05:37,360
That wasn't your money anyway.

124
00:05:38,079 --> 00:05:39,279
Why does it hurt you so much?

125
00:05:40,959 --> 00:05:42,040
Zhang Xiaobei.

126
00:05:47,920 --> 00:05:49,279
I've been wondering all along

127
00:05:50,720 --> 00:05:53,040
why Sheng Yuanzhou suddenly stopped fearing me.

128
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:55,839
And why he was buying the Zhangs a house.

129
00:05:56,839 --> 00:05:57,519
Honestly,

130
00:05:58,279 --> 00:06:00,079
the day you two switched back,

131
00:06:00,519 --> 00:06:01,959
you really had me fooled.

132
00:06:02,519 --> 00:06:04,680
So I purposely had Zhu Yutong test you.

133
00:06:06,360 --> 00:06:08,120
Because the real Sheng Yuanzhou

134
00:06:08,399 --> 00:06:10,920
would never sell his mother's land.

135
00:06:15,079 --> 00:06:16,439
I didn't expect you to actually take the bait.

136
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:19,040
What the hell do you mean?

137
00:06:19,839 --> 00:06:20,720
Nothing.

138
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:22,959
Didn't you use the Key of Fate too

139
00:06:23,439 --> 00:06:26,360
to find out I'm not Sheng Yuanzhou's biological father?

140
00:06:38,800 --> 00:06:39,879
I don't care at all

141
00:06:39,879 --> 00:06:41,519
which one of you is actually Sheng Yuanzhou.

142
00:06:41,839 --> 00:06:43,560
I want an obedient son.

143
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:47,040
On that point,

144
00:06:48,480 --> 00:06:50,279
I suppose Sheng Yuanzhou is more suitable.

145
00:06:51,560 --> 00:06:52,079
Indeed.

146
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:55,160
I've groomed Sheng Yuanzhou since childhood.

147
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:57,439
So his obedience comes naturally.

148
00:06:58,120 --> 00:07:00,360
But I absolutely loathe his cowardice.

149
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:02,920
By contrast,

150
00:07:04,439 --> 00:07:06,759
I actually feel you're more like my son.

151
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:10,279
We both used the Key of Fate to switch identities.

152
00:07:11,199 --> 00:07:12,480
We share a desire for money,

153
00:07:13,279 --> 00:07:14,079
and we're both capable.

154
00:07:14,519 --> 00:07:16,879
No matter how you look at it, it feels like destiny.

155
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:29,040
What's in it for me if I'm your son?

156
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:34,959
After I die,

157
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:37,360
the Shengshi Group will be yours.

158
00:07:39,199 --> 00:07:39,639
What do you say?

159
00:07:41,199 --> 00:07:42,079
Be my son

160
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:44,199
and enjoy all this wealth and glory.

161
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:46,639
I could ask for nothing more.

162
00:07:47,160 --> 00:07:48,600
Switching identities with Sheng Yuanzhou,

163
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:49,920
wasn't it exactly for this?

164
00:07:50,079 --> 00:07:50,800
Good.

165
00:07:51,480 --> 00:07:52,759
But I have one condition.

166
00:07:53,079 --> 00:07:53,839
What condition?

167
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:58,519
Cut all ties with your past.

168
00:07:58,800 --> 00:08:00,000
You're no longer Zhang Xiaobei.

169
00:08:00,560 --> 00:08:02,879
Cut off all contact with your birth parents.

170
00:08:03,480 --> 00:08:05,040
Stop meddling in the Zhang family's business.

171
00:08:05,519 --> 00:08:07,560
If you don't even have that much resolve,

172
00:08:08,519 --> 00:08:10,920
you don't deserve to be my son.

173
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:18,000
Sheng Shizhong.

174
00:08:18,759 --> 00:08:21,279
What exactly is your game here?

175
00:08:27,839 --> 00:08:28,160
Hello?

176
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:29,879
Sheng Yuanzhou, help me!

177
00:08:30,319 --> 00:08:30,920
My dad's missing.

178
00:08:35,519 --> 00:08:38,000
I'm so worried. Where could he be?

179
00:08:38,360 --> 00:08:39,080
Auntie, don't panic.

180
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:40,320
We will definitely find him.

181
00:08:41,639 --> 00:08:43,159
Where did he go? I'm worried sick!

182
00:08:43,159 --> 00:08:43,720
What happened?

183
00:08:43,720 --> 00:08:44,639
How could he just disappear?

184
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:46,120
Why are you here?

185
00:08:51,120 --> 00:08:51,960
Xiaobei's dad...

186
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:53,360
He borrowed money to rent a place,

187
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:55,000
and now the agent is nowhere to be found,

188
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:56,159
and the money is gone.

189
00:08:57,039 --> 00:08:59,360
He grabbed a knife and stormed out.

190
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:00,200
Where's Zhang Xiaobei?

191
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:01,559
He went out looking for him.

192
00:09:02,399 --> 00:09:03,320
But hasn't found him yet.

193
00:09:04,519 --> 00:09:05,039
Yuanzhou,

194
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:07,399
Xiaobei said

195
00:09:07,639 --> 00:09:08,799
you're really capable.

196
00:09:09,120 --> 00:09:10,799
He said you can handle anything.

197
00:09:11,039 --> 00:09:11,840
I'm begging you.

198
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:14,000
You must have a way!

199
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:17,279
He's usually timid but gets hotheaded.

200
00:09:17,519 --> 00:09:19,039
Something terrible is going to happen!

201
00:09:19,399 --> 00:09:20,600
When I was kidnapped before,

202
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:22,000
you found me immediately.

203
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:24,120
You'll have a way this time too, right?

204
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:27,039
Don't worry. Leave it to me.

205
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:36,600
Dad!

206
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:37,720
Dad!

207
00:09:42,320 --> 00:09:43,080
Excuse me.

208
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:47,080
Hello, Siqi.

209
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:47,960
Did you find him?

210
00:09:48,879 --> 00:09:49,159
Hello?

211
00:10:02,279 --> 00:10:03,360
Luo Bing, any news?

212
00:10:03,879 --> 00:10:04,919
Mr. Sheng, we found him.

213
00:10:05,240 --> 00:10:05,679
But...

214
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:08,000
But what?

215
00:10:08,399 --> 00:10:10,159
I'll take you all down with me!

216
00:10:10,480 --> 00:10:11,639
Tell the guy who scammed me to come out!

217
00:10:11,639 --> 00:10:11,879
Okay.

218
00:10:11,879 --> 00:10:12,519
Come out!

219
00:10:12,759 --> 00:10:13,799
I'll get him. I'll go get him!

220
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:15,679
That's my hard-earned money!

221
00:10:15,679 --> 00:10:17,799
My whole family depends on it!

222
00:10:17,919 --> 00:10:18,840
I get it, I get it!

223
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:19,440
Just put the knife down first.

224
00:10:19,440 --> 00:10:19,919
Come out!

225
00:10:20,360 --> 00:10:21,480
Dad, put the knife down!

226
00:10:21,480 --> 00:10:21,960
Stay back!

227
00:10:22,200 --> 00:10:22,639
Put it down, put it down!

228
00:10:22,639 --> 00:10:23,840
Don't do anything stupid. Put it down!

229
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:27,039
It's gone. All my money is gone!

230
00:10:27,240 --> 00:10:28,080
The money isn't important.

231
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:29,480
If the money's gone, we can just earn it back, okay?

232
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:29,919
Put it down.

233
00:10:29,919 --> 00:10:30,600
Nonsense!

234
00:10:31,639 --> 00:10:32,480
Money is everything!

235
00:10:33,080 --> 00:10:34,480
It's because I have no money

236
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:36,399
that my daughter died!

237
00:10:36,799 --> 00:10:38,679
that my son is always bullied!

238
00:10:39,039 --> 00:10:40,919
and my wife always suffers!

239
00:10:41,159 --> 00:10:43,919
It's all because I don't have money!

240
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:47,039
I took out a loan I can't repay,

241
00:10:47,399 --> 00:10:49,600
and now my whole family is ruined!

242
00:10:49,600 --> 00:10:50,399
I have money.

243
00:10:50,399 --> 00:10:51,440
I'll cover you first, okay?

244
00:10:51,840 --> 00:10:52,399
You're lying to me.

245
00:10:52,840 --> 00:10:54,080
We don't even know each other.

246
00:10:54,320 --> 00:10:55,360
Why would you pay me?

247
00:10:55,360 --> 00:10:56,919
Just treat it as a loan from me, okay?

248
00:10:56,919 --> 00:10:57,639
Just put it down.

249
00:10:57,639 --> 00:11:00,000
A loan? You think I'm that easy to fool?

250
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:01,600
You're still lying to me!

251
00:11:01,960 --> 00:11:02,559
Forget it.

252
00:11:03,679 --> 00:11:04,159
I...

253
00:11:05,360 --> 00:11:06,559
There's no point.

254
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:09,519
Only dying will end this once and for all.

255
00:11:09,519 --> 00:11:09,960
What are you doing?

256
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:10,759
My family...

257
00:11:12,480 --> 00:11:12,960
threw up!

258
00:11:14,399 --> 00:11:15,200
To the hospital! To the hospital!

259
00:11:18,200 --> 00:11:18,559
Dad!

260
00:11:21,240 --> 00:11:22,000
Doctor, quick!

261
00:11:22,120 --> 00:11:23,320
Prep a stomach pump. Someone swallowed pills!

262
00:11:23,320 --> 00:11:23,840
Hurry, pump his stomach!

263
00:11:24,279 --> 00:11:24,879
Quick, follow me.

264
00:11:37,759 --> 00:11:38,799
Thank you for saving my dad.

265
00:11:39,559 --> 00:11:40,080
Don't mention it.

266
00:11:41,759 --> 00:11:42,720
It was the right thing to do.

267
00:11:43,960 --> 00:11:46,039
Sheng Yuanzhou, is this your usual trick?

268
00:11:46,320 --> 00:11:47,919
Ruin people first, then play the good guy?

269
00:11:48,080 --> 00:11:49,799
If Shengshi Group hadn't shorted the fund,

270
00:11:49,799 --> 00:11:51,080
my dad wouldn't have tried to kill himself.

271
00:11:52,360 --> 00:11:52,960
What are you doing?

272
00:11:53,200 --> 00:11:54,679
This is a hospital. Keep it down.

273
00:11:55,879 --> 00:11:56,360
Just go.

274
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:58,360
We don't need you here.

275
00:12:23,120 --> 00:12:23,759
I've thought it through.

276
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:25,919
I accept your terms.

277
00:12:27,320 --> 00:12:28,960
I'll cut all ties with the Zhang family.

278
00:12:29,440 --> 00:12:30,399
But you have to promise

279
00:12:30,399 --> 00:12:31,879
to name me the heir to the group.

280
00:12:33,960 --> 00:12:34,600
Deal.

281
00:12:35,159 --> 00:12:36,279
As long as you pass my test.

282
00:12:36,840 --> 00:12:38,039
As the first step,

283
00:12:38,320 --> 00:12:40,399
I need you to acquire the shares of Benevolent Medical.

284
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:41,559
Got it.

285
00:12:42,159 --> 00:12:43,639
I won't let you down.

286
00:12:51,120 --> 00:12:52,559
Dad, you're awake.

287
00:12:53,320 --> 00:12:55,039
Old Zhang, you're awake.

288
00:12:55,960 --> 00:12:56,759
I...

289
00:12:58,080 --> 00:12:59,799
You scared me to death.

290
00:13:00,240 --> 00:13:02,399
I just didn't want to burden you all.

291
00:13:03,240 --> 00:13:05,000
Don't be silly.

292
00:13:05,279 --> 00:13:06,399
If you were gone...

293
00:13:06,399 --> 00:13:08,279
how would Xiaobei and I go on?

294
00:13:08,720 --> 00:13:09,159
Dad.

295
00:13:10,159 --> 00:13:11,120
We're family.

296
00:13:11,399 --> 00:13:12,559
We'll face any problem together.

297
00:13:12,679 --> 00:13:13,480
That's right.

298
00:13:16,559 --> 00:13:17,159
Zhang Qiang.

299
00:13:17,600 --> 00:13:18,399
Where's Zhang Qiang?

300
00:13:20,799 --> 00:13:21,399
Who are you?

301
00:13:21,799 --> 00:13:23,000
Who are you?

302
00:13:23,240 --> 00:13:24,159
I'm Zhang Qiang's son.

303
00:13:24,480 --> 00:13:26,120
I'm your dad's creditor.

304
00:13:26,480 --> 00:13:28,120
Your dad owes us 100,000 yuan.

305
00:13:29,159 --> 00:13:31,279
Here's the IOU. Take a good look.

306
00:13:31,279 --> 00:13:32,879
I'll take responsibility for my own actions.

307
00:13:32,879 --> 00:13:34,879
Do whatever you want with my old bones.

308
00:13:35,039 --> 00:13:36,600
Just leave my son alone.

309
00:13:36,960 --> 00:13:39,039
Got some nerve, old man.

310
00:13:39,639 --> 00:13:40,519
What are you doing?

311
00:13:40,519 --> 00:13:41,320
Stay away from my dad.

312
00:13:41,600 --> 00:13:43,840
What, trying to weasel out of your debt?

313
00:13:44,559 --> 00:13:45,360
I've got money.

314
00:13:47,159 --> 00:13:47,879
100,000 yuan.

315
00:13:52,200 --> 00:13:53,000
The money my dad owes...

316
00:13:54,080 --> 00:13:54,639
I'll pay you back.

317
00:13:57,919 --> 00:13:59,879
You've got some backbone, kid.

318
00:14:01,279 --> 00:14:01,799
Three days.

319
00:14:03,159 --> 00:14:03,960
Give me three days.

320
00:14:04,159 --> 00:14:05,120
No.

321
00:14:05,840 --> 00:14:06,720
You get one day.

322
00:14:07,159 --> 00:14:08,039
If you don't have the money,

323
00:14:09,279 --> 00:14:11,000
don't blame me for getting nasty.

324
00:14:29,039 --> 00:14:30,039
At a time like this,

325
00:14:30,039 --> 00:14:31,879
why won't you accept my help?

326
00:14:32,360 --> 00:14:33,720
Why are you still so proud?

327
00:14:33,960 --> 00:14:35,320
It's not about pride.

328
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:37,840
I just don't want to lose.

329
00:14:38,159 --> 00:14:38,879
I want to prove to you

330
00:14:38,879 --> 00:14:40,559
that I'm the one who can protect you.

331
00:14:41,039 --> 00:14:42,320
He saved you when you were kidnapped.

332
00:14:42,759 --> 00:14:44,240
He also saved my dad from suicide.

333
00:14:45,200 --> 00:14:47,120
But he's the root cause of all this.

334
00:14:47,840 --> 00:14:48,480
This time,

335
00:14:49,159 --> 00:14:50,679
I want to solve the problem my way.

336
00:14:52,720 --> 00:14:54,919
Xiaobei, it's not what you think.

337
00:14:56,240 --> 00:14:58,519
Siqi, this time I want to do it myself.

338
00:15:00,279 --> 00:15:01,120
Just let me handle it.

339
00:15:01,600 --> 00:15:02,759
Move along.

340
00:15:03,759 --> 00:15:05,120
I really need this job.

341
00:15:05,639 --> 00:15:06,879
Please give me this chance.

342
00:15:07,240 --> 00:15:08,399
My family used to sell jianbing.

343
00:15:08,559 --> 00:15:09,679
I know how to work in a kitchen.

344
00:15:10,000 --> 00:15:12,320
We need diplomas, degrees, and experience.

345
00:15:12,320 --> 00:15:13,039
You've got none of that.

346
00:15:13,039 --> 00:15:14,080
Why should I hire you?

347
00:15:14,080 --> 00:15:15,440
I actually went to college.

348
00:15:16,000 --> 00:15:16,639
AI programming.

349
00:15:17,039 --> 00:15:17,879
And I know antique appraisal.

350
00:15:18,120 --> 00:15:19,840
We only look at diplomas.

351
00:15:20,159 --> 00:15:21,519
You were expelled.

352
00:15:21,759 --> 00:15:22,960
I definitely can't give you a full-time job.

353
00:15:24,320 --> 00:15:25,519
Temp or part-time would be fine.

354
00:15:25,960 --> 00:15:27,000
I really need money.

355
00:15:27,159 --> 00:15:28,519
How many times have I told you?

356
00:15:28,519 --> 00:15:29,799
We don't need anyone!

357
00:15:45,080 --> 00:15:45,840
Master Long invites you.

358
00:15:53,000 --> 00:15:53,799
You are...?

359
00:15:55,759 --> 00:15:56,799
You don't remember me?

360
00:15:59,720 --> 00:16:01,080
The old man buying the painting.

361
00:16:02,159 --> 00:16:02,639
Have a seat.

362
00:16:06,679 --> 00:16:07,360
Young man,

363
00:16:08,480 --> 00:16:10,519
inviting you here so suddenly today,

364
00:16:11,200 --> 00:16:12,240
I just wanted you to

365
00:16:13,000 --> 00:16:14,519
do me a little favor.

366
00:16:15,080 --> 00:16:16,919
I've got two items here.

367
00:16:17,399 --> 00:16:18,519
I'd like you to take a look.

368
00:16:19,159 --> 00:16:19,960
And tell me if they're authentic.

369
00:16:21,480 --> 00:16:23,440
I'm not a pro at this.

370
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:25,639
No matter.

371
00:16:26,600 --> 00:16:27,559
Just speak your mind.

372
00:16:30,440 --> 00:16:31,559
This blue and white porcelain is fake.

373
00:16:34,399 --> 00:16:35,360
Why do you say that?

374
00:16:35,879 --> 00:16:36,320
Look.

375
00:16:37,519 --> 00:16:39,360
The blue glaze is too pale,

376
00:16:39,559 --> 00:16:40,240
you can see right through it.

377
00:16:40,519 --> 00:16:42,120
And the line tracing is quite stiff.

378
00:16:42,480 --> 00:16:44,519
The color lacks depth.

379
00:16:45,080 --> 00:16:46,159
It looks quite superficial overall.

380
00:16:48,559 --> 00:16:49,600
This painting is fake too.

381
00:16:50,279 --> 00:16:51,200
But it's worth a lot.

382
00:16:51,720 --> 00:16:54,200
A fake can be worth a lot?

383
00:16:54,639 --> 00:16:55,720
The original is from the Song dynasty,

384
00:16:55,960 --> 00:16:57,080
but this is a Qing dynasty imitation.

385
00:16:57,799 --> 00:16:58,720
So it's still valuable.

386
00:17:00,960 --> 00:17:02,759
Impressive, impressive.

387
00:17:03,480 --> 00:17:05,519
You were spot on with both.

388
00:17:06,039 --> 00:17:06,720
You've studied this?

389
00:17:07,359 --> 00:17:07,759
No.

390
00:17:08,359 --> 00:17:10,000
I was just guessing.

391
00:17:10,279 --> 00:17:11,279
It was pure luck.

392
00:17:13,039 --> 00:17:14,079
Interesting.

393
00:17:14,440 --> 00:17:16,559
Do you want to learn antique appraisal?

394
00:17:18,519 --> 00:17:19,640
Antique appraisal?

395
00:17:22,440 --> 00:17:23,039
Not interested.

396
00:17:25,960 --> 00:17:27,559
Don't rush to say no.

397
00:17:27,920 --> 00:17:29,240
Think it over carefully.

398
00:17:31,680 --> 00:17:33,319
A disciple of the Long family

399
00:17:34,000 --> 00:17:35,960
isn't something just anyone can be.

400
00:17:42,279 --> 00:17:42,920
That's all.

401
00:17:46,039 --> 00:17:47,519
How's the money coming?

402
00:17:50,680 --> 00:17:51,480
No money.

403
00:17:51,799 --> 00:17:52,440
No money?

404
00:17:52,960 --> 00:17:55,200
Then let that pretty little slut pay for you!

405
00:17:55,599 --> 00:17:56,680
Watch your mouth.

406
00:17:56,839 --> 00:17:58,839
And if I don't?

407
00:17:58,839 --> 00:18:00,000
Not only is my mouth filthy,

408
00:18:00,240 --> 00:18:01,200
my hands are itching too.
